From: James Clark <james.clark@linaro.org>
Date: Wed, 8 Jan 2025 14:29:00 +0000
Subject: perf tests arm_spe: Add test for discard mode
Git-commit: 05cd60e4d0716ecc1a8027ae782c25522292d6ef
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

Add a test that checks that there were no AUX or AUXTRACE events
recorded when discard mode is used.

